    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You command your Pod to execute an advanced set of processes for the next minute, selecting two of the following benefits to gain for the duration of this jutsu:</p><ul><li><strong>Traversal Protocol:</strong> While attached to your Pod, you ignore difficult terrain and movement speed reductions that are not the result of conditions. Additionally, you can travel at Fast pace with no penalty.</li><li><strong>Observation Protocol:</strong> You intertwine and bolster your senses with your Pod, sharing your special senses, gaining the ability to see through up to 5 feet of obstruction, and gaining advantage on Intelligence or Wisdom skill checks.</li><li><strong>Stealth Protocol:</strong> Your Pod projects a subtle field of transparent energy, blending you with the terrain around you. You and allied creatures within 15 feet of you gain a +1d8 bonus to Stealth checks, and can move at full speed while hiding. Additionally, allies do not need to remake Stealth checks for the duration unless discovered.</li></ul>",
